\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Transformer-Based Multi-Modal Trajectory Prediction\
\
This project implements a **Transformer-based model for pedestrian trajectory prediction** using the **nuScenes dataset**.\
\
The model predicts the **future 3 seconds of motion** given **2 seconds of past trajectory**.\
\
## Features\
\
- Transformer-based temporal modeling\
- Multi-modal trajectory prediction\
- ADE / FDE evaluation metrics\
- Visualization of predictions\
- Animated trajectory demonstrations\
\
## Dataset\
\
nuScenes v1.0-mini dataset.\
\
Agents are represented using:\
\
- x position\
- y position\
- x velocity\
- y velocity\
\
